reviewText: I've been looking for this video forever! It had some footage I didn't expect, such as a Bull Elk playing around with what looks like a stump on its antlers. One piece of footage, which was what Jim Shockey called a deer hunter's worst nightmare, was when a hunter from Alberta, Canada, encountered an absolute monster of a whitetail and he had a doe tag. That deer was absolutely huge, but one way to look at it, he'll be bigger next year.
